{"tid":763582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【炒賣月餅】男子被呃買假月餅券 損失6000元","createTime":"2018-08-01T08:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T12:04:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"866b473fc181a9eced082bf2399108cf5af96144","tid":763582,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180801/_2018080115264081972.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180801%2F_2018080115264081972.jpg&h=53ee8ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美心推出第二輪流心奶黃月餅，再度引起大批市民搶購。上水一名男子今早到場以月餅券換購時，始知手持的兌換券屬偽造，於是報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n事發在今早9時13分，一名男子手持5張共值6000港元的月餅券，到龍運街8號美心餅店，準備兌換同等價值的流心奶黃月餅。惟職員表示該批月餅券屬偽造，男子始知上當受騙，於是報警，警方正調查案件。<br />\n<br />\n美心早前推出流心奶黃月餅一度賣斷市，內地甚至出現月餅券的炒風，不少市民購買後隨即在網上放售，部分價格甚至較原價貴一倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/780100-香港-【炒賣月餅】男子被呃買假月餅券+損失6000元\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F780100-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E7%82%92%E8%B3%A3%E6%9C%88%E9%A4%85%E3%80%91%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%83%E8%B2%B7%E5%81%87%E6%9C%88%E9%A4%85%E5%88%B8%2B%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B16000%E5%85%83&d=LDTxD5OmsASDaJfIw5fsuk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=8aa2b135\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F780100-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E7%82%92%E8%B3%A3%E6%9C%88%E9%A4%85%E3%80%91%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%83%E8%B2%B7%E5%81%87%E6%9C%88%E9%A4%85%E5%88%B8%2B%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B16000%E5%85%83&h=5606f40c\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/780100-香港-【炒賣月餅】男子被呃買假月餅券+損失6000元</a>"},{"pid":"a2506dceceeb11f8c259cec74f5b4db4c5911dba","tid":763582,"uid":17646,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T08:47:09.000Z","msg":"5張6000蚊？<br />\n流心奶皇唔係2